## SavedObjectsCreateOptions.initialNamespaces property

Optional initial namespaces for the object to be created in. If this is defined, it will supersede the namespace ID that is in [SavedObjectsCreateOptions](./opensearch-dashboards.savedobjectscreateoptions.md)<!-- -->.

Note: this can only be used for multi-namespace object types.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
initialNamespaces?: string[];
```
